## Core Workflow
1. **Baseline Boot**: Device boots from immutable, signed baseline (TPM-sealed or secure boot)
2. **Regional Bootstrap**: Device attests to nearest regional bootstrap service over constrained network
3. **CSR Enrollment**: Device submits CSR to central KCA with attested identity
4. **Certificate Issuance**: KCA issues 600s TTL TLS cert bound to SPIFFE ID (e.g., spiffe://retail.acme.com/store-042/device-sensor-17) with 'edge-retail' scope
5. **Policy Binding**: Certificate includes embedded policy claims for model-signing authorization

## Code Example
